metadata.name: FSC Golden Ticket #001
metadata.description: Fluffy Slugs Club (FSC) Golden Ticket. This token is a limited community offering that provides slightly more features for its holder. 1. Receive multiple gift tokens at once from subsequent collections of the FSC community. 2. Rarity integration (each token is numbered). 3. Separate draws among FSC Golden Ticket holders. Our history of NFT community development started with your help. We appreciate it.
